============================================================
AO CHAT
============================================================


Python implementation of Anarchy Online Chat protocol.


TABLE OF CONTENTS:
==================
I.  Installation.
II. Anarhy Online chat protocol.
III. About author.


I. INSTALLATION
===============
Please, run these commands in command line to install AOChat python package:
~$ cd <path/to/aochat/sources>
~$ python setup.py build
~$ sudo python setup.py install


II. ANARCHY ONLINE CHAT PROTOCOL
================================

1. DATA TYPES
-------------
Integer = [ 4 bytes ]
String = [ 2 bytes of length of string ] + [ string ]
ChannelID = [ 5 bytes ]
IntegerTuple = [ 2 bytes of count of items ] + [ 1st Integer ] + [ 2nd Integer ] + ...
StringTuple = [ 2 bytes of count of items ] + [ 1st String ] + [ 2nd String ] + ...

2. PACKETS: GENERAL
-------------------
packet = [ 2 bytes of type ] + [ 2 bytes of length of data ] + [ data ]

